Program: Omnibus
Title: The Swap - Norbert Reinhardt
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376lz4
Last Broadcast Date: 07 September 1999
The story of how FARC (Revolutionary Armed Forces of Colombia, a Marxist rebel group) kidnapped Canadian mining company employee Ed Leonard, then traded him for Norbert Reinhardt, a company executive who felt compelled to take Leonard's place.